articles.title: 'JOAO FELIX IS JUST A PASSENGER ON THE TEAM!' 😮 - Stevie Nicol on lackluster Barca | ESPN FC - ESPN UK
articles.description: Luis Garcia, Shaka Hislop and Steve Nicol join Dan Thomas on ESPN FC to react to Barcelona's lackluster 4-2 win over Real Betis then preview the Copa del Rey...
